\f2\fs18 \cf3 \super 9\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Joshua said to the Israelites, \'93Come here and listen to the words of the\'a0Lord\'a0your God.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 10\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub This is how you will know that the living God\'a0is among you\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I\'92ve said it from day 1 \'96 this is about faith and not money.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Today God is going to show up in a big way!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But we wanted a number that would prove God is with us\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Illustration of Injoy telling us we could raise if we were good \'96 we could raise around $240,000 over 3 years.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Last week we had a dinner with all of our BOLD Volunteers\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We took up an early pledge because I believe leaders go first!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And when leaders go first it makes it easier for others to follow.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So how much do you think just 33 families in our church were able to pledge?  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}OVER $270,000\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I\'92m telling you this so you are motivated\'85not demotivated!\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl2\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If your first reaction is \'96 Great\'85now I don\'92t have to give.  You\'92ve missed the point.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This whole thing has been about a number God has put in your heart to give.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Our number is just a number\'85there\'92s nothing magical about it and we know we needed more we obviously didn\'92t have big enough faith.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We will be successful when everyone, plays their role and gives sacrificially\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}See I talked earlier about that moment of truth where someone had some circumstances change and it was tempting to change the conversation\'85but the only conversation that matters is the one you have with God.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}(sit here a little more with this)\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 and that he will certainly drive out before you the Canaanites, Hittites,\'a0Hivites, Perizzites, Girgashites, Amorites and Jebusites.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There are still some battles before us after\'85this is the beginning not the end of the journey.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you see your life as a series of steps then you\'92ll be ok\'85knowing you\'92re going from one battle/step to the next\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you think you\'92ll get to a place where you\'92ll be fine, no more problems financially, relationally, spiritually, you\'92re going to struggle.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4  \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf3 \super 13\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub And as soon as the priests who carry the ark of the\'a0Lord\'97the Lord of all the earth\'97set foot in the Jordan, its waters flowing downstream\'a0will be cut off\'a0and stand\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is so fascinating to me because they\'92ve been here before.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The nation has stood at the edge and the ledge of water before waiting for God to do a miracle?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Can you think of when?\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Yeah, roughly 40 years before when Pharaoh was coming after them they were in the same spot\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And God parted the Red Sea and they walked across dry land!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They are doing it again!  \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We\'92ve been singing this song the whole series \'93Do it again\'94 by elevation church because as a church I feel we\'92re in the same place we were roughly 3 years ago.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I wonder how many people thought God was going to do the same thing?\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Standing there waiting for God to part the river.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But this time is different.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This time God says\'85you go first.  I went first last time and your faith grew.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But if I keep doing the same miracles you won\'92t grow\'85so you go first!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If your next step looks like your previous step you\'92re not moving\'85you\'92re just walking in place!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf3 \super 14\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub So when the people broke camp to cross the Jordan, the priests carrying the ark of the covenant\'a0went ahead\'a0of them.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 15\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Now the Jordan\'a0is at flood stage\'a0all during harvest.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I find it interesting that God chose for them to cross during flood stage!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You didn\'92t think this would be easy did you?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You didn\'92t think God would set it up so it looks possible.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}NO\'85he set it up in such a way so that when it happens the ONLY explanation is God was a part of it!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 Yet as soon as the priests who carried the ark reached the Jordan and their feet touched the water\'92s edge,\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 16\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub the water from upstream stopped flowing.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The miracle happened only after they went first!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \'a0It piled up in a heap\'a0a great distance away, at a town called Adam in the vicinity of Zarethan,\'a0while the water flowing down\'a0to the Sea of the Arabah\'a0(that is, the Dead Sea) was completely cut off.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I find it fascinating that God chose to wall up the water a great distance away\'85not right in front of them.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Can you image what the people in that town thought?  They had a miracle too?  They experienced God in a unique way because God\'92s people were faithful\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This was 30 miles upstream.  God made dry land for roughly 30 miles!  Extreme excess to prove a point.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We have no clue what miracles happened in thief life because of the faithfulness that was happening in thiers.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0
\f4\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You have no clue what miracles God is going to do in others lives because of the faithfulness of yours!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When God\'92s people take big steps of faith it resonates miles around into areas that may not even know God yet.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0
\f3\b0 \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Our churches vision is to have such an impact that people who don\'92t even know God yet can\'92t help but notice what God is doing because it\'92s impact them too!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 So the people crossed over opposite Jericho.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 17\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub The priests\'a0who carried the ark of the covenant of the\'a0Lord\'a0stopped in the middle of the Jordan and stood on dry ground,\'a0while all Israel passed by until the whole nation had completed the crossing on dry ground.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0
\f0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The miracle happened!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And today\'85a miracle is going to happen!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God did it again.  He was faithful and it was amazing!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs36 \cf3 4\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 When the whole nation had finished crossing the Jordan,\'a0the\'a0Lord\'a0said to Joshua,\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 2\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub \'93Choose twelve men\'a0from among the people, one from each tribe,\
\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}That is important\'85because a tribe is like a family!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 3\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub and tell them to take up twelve stones\'a0from the middle of the Jordan,\'a0from right where the priests are standing, and carry them over with you and put them down at the place where you stay tonight.\'94\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 In the future, when your children\'a0ask you, \'91What do these stones mean?\'92\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf3 \super 7\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub tell them that the flow of the Jordan was cut off\'a0before the ark of the covenant of the\'a0Lord. When it crossed the Jordan, the waters of the Jordan were cut off. These stones are to be a memorial\'a0to the people of Israel forever.\'94\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl0
\f0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So this what we\'92re going to do today.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I know today is going to be an amazing day\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And every one of you represents a tribe in our church family!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
